&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:8pt; font-weight:400;&quot;&gt;Select the folder containing videos that have already been analyzed by DeepLabCut.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:8pt; font-weight:400;&quot;&gt;The software will use the corresponding tracking outputs (e.g., CSV files with pose coordinates) to generate annotated videos with overlaid body part positions.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:8pt; font-weight:400; font-style:italic;&quot;&gt;Ensure that the tracking files match the videos in name and location.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
